      "input": {"operation":"render_html","palette":"xterm","text":"\u001b[94;2mlightblue and also faint[a specific Unicode escape sequence representing the ANSI reset command — ask the implementation team for the exact character sequence]"},
      "expected_output": "<span style=\"color: #4682B4;\"><span style=\"font-weight: lighter;\">lightblue and also faint</span></span>"
    }
  ]
}
```

